title: The Arrhythmias Big Band
text:
Story Published: Oct 2, 2015 at 12:24 PM EDT Story Updated: Oct 2, 2015 at 12:24 PM EDT 
At the Ausbury United Methodist Church 
325 Franklin Street 
Watertown, Doors open at 5:45 pm 
We will perform familiar big band swing music for dancing and listening on Friday, October 2, at Asbury United Methodist Church, 327 Franklin Street, Watertown. The 7-9 p.m. performance will be preceded by free swing dancing lessons taught by Maria and Tom Cesta from 5:30-7 p.m. downstairs in Wesley Hall at the church. 
Tickets are $8 and are available in Watertown at Asbury Church, Boltonâ€™s Pharmacy, 128 West Main St.; the Urban Mission, 247 Factory Street and Aamco Transmission, 595 Coffeen St. For more information, please call 782-3240.
